User: I'm looking at how to extract the file ID from the given URL. It seems like the ID is part of the path, like in https://drive.google.com/file/d/1WKOUjkKCUUBQv7u3hlwPvTLdyTIcf1fm/view.

Grok: The file ID is "1WKOUjkKCUUBQv7u3hlwPvTLdyTIcf1fm." I can use this to build a download link, like https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&id=1WKOUjkKCUUBQv7u3hlwPvTLdyTIcf1fm.
